                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="u-caption u-section__part u-section__part--large">The physical world will become a treasure trove of information. Whether you’re visiting popular landmarks or wondering what a specific plant is, the answer will be in front of your eyes. Searching for specific items, such as clothes or furniture, will be easier as the physical item becomes your search. The increased access to information will act as a guide to reality, customised by your own preferences. No longer needing to switch attention between a screen and the physical world makes interactions feel intuitive. The use of APIs and decentralisation ensures the platform’s openness, and helps to maintain the community driven control.</p>
